<section id="rules">
<h2><span class="label">Section 10</span>Local Rules &amp; Filing Fees</h2>
<p>Statutory federal filing fees are uniform across all US bankruptcy districts: $338 for Chapter 7, $313 for Chapter 13, $1,738 for Chapter 11, and $278 for Chapter 12 (current as of 2025). S.D. Miss. administers its local rules at the following location:</p>
